Holly Willoughby ta bar Peter Jones, tauraron fim din Dragons Den, da mummunan sakamako ta hanyar barin wani kamfani mai shahararren salon rayuwa a lokacin karshe don mayar da hankali kan sabbin yarjejeniyoyi masu kyau tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
