Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia da kuma YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai gudanar da tarurruka da dama, na farko kuwa a wannan daren ne a garin Wheeling da ke jihar West Virginia.
Yana ɗaya daga cikin tarurruka biyar da ake shirin yi a mako mai zuwa, inda zai tsaya a wurare da yawa da abokansa suke zuwa, har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka dage zaben tabbatar da zaben sabon alkalin kotun koli, Trump na shirin karawa jam'iyyar goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisa a lokacin zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi zaben Trump a West Virginia, kuma ta yaya za a iya kallonsa a kan layi?
Taron Trump a birnin Wheeling, West Virginia, zai fara a karfe 7:00 na yammacin wannan daren, ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube a ƙasa.
Trump ya yi jawabi a kotun da aka yanke wa mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi zaben shugaban kasa, inda aka yi tashin hankali kan zargin da ake yi masa na lalata da 'yan mata, amma an dage zaben da za a amince da shi a matsayin mai shari'a har tsawon mako guda, yayin da hukumar FBI ke binciken zargin.
Amma babban manufar tarurrukan Trump shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu ci gaba, yayin da suke fuskantar zaɓe mai wuya a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, sanarwar kamfen din Trump ta ce, tarurruka biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, za su yi ne don "sanya masu sa kai da masu goyon baya a cikin wani tashin hankali da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma karawa da rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisa", in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
"Samun iko da majalisa na da muhimmanci ga shirin shugaban kasa, don haka zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a lokacin da ake shirin fara yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump a Reuters.
Za a yi taron a filin wasa na Wesbanco a birnin Wheeling, kuma ana sa ran masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania za su halarci taron, kuma ana sa ran cewa 'yan jarida daga Pittsburgh za su ba da rahoto, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na West Virginia Metro News.
Taron na ranar Asabar zai zama ziyarar Trump ta biyu a wannan watan a jihar ta West Virginia, inda ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump na son ya goyi bayan Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar 'yan Republican a West Virginia, amma yana kasa a zaben.
"Ba abu mai kyau ba ne ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya yi kokarin kara masa karbuwa", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA na nuna himma don ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a gasar cin kofin duniya ta 'yan wasa a ranar Lahadi
Bayan an yi zagaye uku, wasan hudu da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma zai iya zama daidai abin da ake bukata a wannan gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Dandalin nasara shi ne tunanin da 'yan wasa suka ƙirƙira kuma suka gaskata da shi, kuma ba fiye da yadda suke yi a gasar da ta kama wannan ba.
A ina ne za su ce nasara ta kasance a yanzu?
"Sun ci gaba da maki shida, yanzu kuma maki hudu, don haka nasara ta fi mana kyau a yanzu, ina tsammanin", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da ya fara gasar yau.
Turai tana kan gaba, a bayyane take, ta kai maki huɗu, tare da wasu goma sha biyu a gaba.
'Yan wasan Amurka, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna ganin suna da ɗan iska a cikin jiragen ruwa kuma suna iya jin tsoron abubuwa da yawa, ba kalla ba ga yanayin Spieth da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka yi wasa tare a duk rana kuma kowannensu ya sami maki uku daga huɗu.
Spieth ya yi nasara sosai wajen kafa misali mai kyau.
Muryar jama'a ta tashi yayin da yake kan hanyar da'irar, kuma ya sanya muhimmiyar bugawa don kula da maki huɗu na wasan bayan shi da Thomas sun kasance maki biyu a baya bayan wasanni biyu.
Ƙwallon da ya ba su tabbacin nasara a wasan a kan rami na 15 ya ba da irin wannan murna, irin murya da ke gaya maka cewa yana da tabbacin cewa tawagar Amirka za ta ci nasara.
"Ya kamata mutum ya yi zurfin tunani kuma ya yi tunanin nasa wasa", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da 'yan wasan za su iya yi a yanzu.
18 ramuka don lashe a cikin maki.
'Yan wasan da suka fi Spieth da Thomas a wasan na kwana biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinaro da Tommy Fleetwood, wanda ba a iya shakkar tarihin Ryder ba.
Wannan ma'aurata da ke Turai sun ci wasanni huɗu kuma ba za su iya yin kuskure ba.
Moliwood su ne kawai ma'aurata da suka samu makaranta a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma kuma sun samu damar kauce wa makaranta a ranar Asabar da safe, da yammacin ranar Juma'a, da kuma filin wasa mai ramuka tara a ranar Juma'a da safe.
Wasan da kuma yadda suke da kuzari suna zuwa da kuma fita daga cikin taron jama'a ya nuna cewa su ne za su yi nasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari, wanda rana ta haskaka a filin wasa na Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau su yi hakan a lokaci ɗaya a ramuka dabam dabam.
Amma, ba shi da sauƙi a ce 'yan Turai ne za su ci.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi wasa da Sergio Garcia, gwarzon wasan da safe, inda ya buga da Alex Noren.
A cikin rami tara na farko, wani ɗan wasa da kuma wasu biyu sun haƙa ɗan wasan Spain da kuma ɗan wasan Sweden a cikin ramin da ba za su iya fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya taimaka maka ka fita daga cikin ramin da kake ciki.
Wasan kwallon kafa da wasan wasan kwallon kafa suna da ban sha'awa sosai domin suna da ma'amala tsakanin ma'aurata, suna ba da shawara, ba sa ba da shawara, kuma yadda tsarin wasan zai iya canzawa a cikin ɗan lokaci.
Turai ta fice a matsayin tawagar da ta yi wasa a baya kuma tana da babban ci gaba a ranar karshe, amma wannan wasan na kwata-kwata ya kuma nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da karfin gwagwarmaya wanda wasu suka yi shakku da shi, musamman sauran Amurkawa.
Turai ta yi nasara da maki 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder
Turai za ta yi nasara sosai a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan wasan kwata-kwata da kuma wasan hudu na ranar Asabar, inda za ta yi nasara da Amurka da ci 10 da 6.
'Yan wasan kwallon kafa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci harin ne da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods, wanda ke fama da matsalar, kuma ya samu maki hudu a filin wasa na Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Thomas Bjorn ta Turai, wadda ke neman ta sake lashe kofin da ta yi a filin wasa na Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka shige, ta yi nasara sosai a kan tawagar Amurka a wasan kwata-kwata da suka yi da safe, inda suka ci 3-1.
Amurka ta fi nuna juriya a wasan hudu, inda ta ci wasanni biyu amma ba ta iya cin nasara ba.
'Yan wasan Jim Furyks sun bukaci maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na musamman a ranar Lahadi domin ci gaba da gasar.
Fleetwood shine farkon sabon dan wasan Turai da ya ci nasara sau hudu a jere, kuma shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Molliwood" bayan babban karshen mako, sune kawai na biyu da suka ci nasara sau hudu daga wasanninsu na farko a tarihin Ryder.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwata-kwata, sun nuna babbar kungiya kuma sun ci Woods da dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau 5-4.
Woods, wanda ya yi nasara a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna kwarewarsa a lokutan da ba a saba gani ba, amma yanzu ya rasa wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 a wasannin da ya buga a wasan kwallon kwando da na hudu, kuma daga cikin wadannan wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda aka yi wa al'ada a wasan kwata-kwata na safiyar yau, ya koma tare da abokin wasansa, Henrik Stenson a wasan kwata-kwata, inda suka ci Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka da ci 2-1 - wadanda suke matsayi na daya da na uku a jerin manyan 'yan wasan golf na duniya.
Amma, ba dukan Turai ba ne suka ji daɗi a wannan rana mai sanyi da kuma sanyi a kudu maso yammacin birnin Paris.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka ci gasar cin kofin duniya sau uku, sun ci wa 'yan wasan Amurkawa kwallo biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sha wahala 2-1 a kan Jon Rahm na Spain da Ian Poulter a wasan kwata-kwata, kuma daga baya suka dawo suka doke Poulter da Rory Mcllroy 4-3 a wasan kwata-kwata bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup cewa ƙungiya ta sami nasara ta hanyar ƙimar maki huɗu a farkon gasar mutum, kodayake ƙungiyar Furyks tana buƙatar daidaitawa kawai don ci gaba da gasar.
Amma, bayan sun yi kwanaki biyu a matsayin na biyu, kamar dai an kai musu hari a ranar Lahadi.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta iya samun damar kawar da makamai ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa, ci gaba da haramcin kasuwanci zai kara kara musu rashin amincewa da Amurka, kuma ba zai yiwu kasar ta kawar da makaman nukiliya ba a irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki matakai masu yawa na nuna kyakkyawar niyya a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya, rufe filin gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin dakatar da ci gaban makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani irin martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, babu tabbacin tsaro na kasarmu, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, ba zai yiwu ba mu cire makaman nukiliya da kanmu".
Ko da yake Ri ya maimaita takunkumin da aka saba yi a Koriya ta Arewa game da kin amincewar Washington da tsarin sauya sheka na kawar da makaman nukiliya, inda ake ganin an saka wa Koriya ta Arewa duk wani mataki da ta dauka, wannan sanarwa ta zama na musamman saboda ba ya musanta kawar da makaman nukiliya kai tsaye kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da kalaman da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai ci da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa, a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, inda Kim ya yi kira ga "aikin kawar da makaman nukiliya daga Koriya ta Kudu" kuma Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta nemi hanyar kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta ajiye makaman nukiliya da farko.
Har ila yau, Washington ta yi tsayayya da kira ga sassauta takunkumin kasuwanci mai tsanani kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Ƙasashen sun bukaci a fara kawar da makaman nukiliya, kuma sun ƙara matsa lamba ta hanyar haramta cinikayya don cimma burinsu, har ma sun yi adawa da sanarwar kawo karshen yaƙin", in ji Ri.
"Mutanen da ba su san kome ba game da mu ne kawai suke mafarkin cewa haramta kasuwanci zai iya kawo mana hari.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da hana kasuwanci yana ƙara sa mu rashin amincewa.
Ri bai ambaci wani shiri na wani taron Kim da Trump ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi magana a majalisar dattijai a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya yi magana game da tarurruka uku da Kim ya yi da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-In a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kuma kara da cewa: Idan jam'iyyar da ke wannan batun na kawar da makaman nukiliya ita ce Koriya ta Kudu maimakon Amurka, ba za a sami wannan matsala ba a batun kawar da makaman nukiliya a Koriya ta Kudu.
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na shekarar da ta gabata lokacin da ya fada a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba makawa ne a yi harin makami mai linzami daga Koriya ta Arewa zuwa Amurka bayan da "Shugaba Trump" ya kira Kim "mai kisan kai".
A bara Trump ya yi barazanar kashe Koriya ta Arewa, amma a wannan shekarar ya yaba wa Kim a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya saboda ƙarfin zuciyarsa wajen ɗaukar mataki na kawar da makaman, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi, kuma haramcin kasuwanci zai ci gaba har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da dukkan makaman nukiliyarta.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da wani lokaci a kan wannan batu, ya ce: "Ko shekara biyu, ko uku, ko watanni biyar - ba kome".
China da Rasha sun ce ya kamata kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya saka wa Pyongyang bisa matakin da ta dauka.
Amma, a ranar Alhamis, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: "Taron Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya hana cinikayya har sai an tabbatar da cikakken kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya amince da karawa Koriya ta Arewa haramcin cinikayya tun daga 2006 a kokarin da ake yi na hana Pyongyang samun kudade don shirin nukiliya da makaman nukiliya.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, inda ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya wani taro.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ziyararsa ta karshe ba ta yi nasara ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu nasara, amma sa'o'i kadan bayan haka, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi masa Allah wadai da yin wasu 'da'awar da ba su dace ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a taron da Moon ya yi a wannan watan cewa za ta rushe sansanonin makamai masu linzami da na nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakin da ya dace.
Ya ce Kim ya ce wa kansa cewa "matakan da ya ke nema" su ne tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawarinsa a Singapore da kuma matakan da ya kamata a dauka don daidaita dangantakar da ke tsakanin kasar da Washington.
Dalibai a Harvard Sun Yi Nazarin Hutu
Wani sabon bincike a Harvard ya ba wa dukan ɗalibai ƙarin barci a ƙoƙarin ƙin ƙyale ɗalibai su riƙa yin barci da dare kuma su yi nazari da taimakon maganin kafeyin.
Wani bincike ya nuna cewa ɗalibai a manyan jami'o'i a duniya ba su san kome ba game da yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin barci a Makarantar Kiwon Lafiya ta Harvard da kuma gwani a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya tsara wannan tsarin, kuma ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a ƙasar Amirka.
Ya soma wannan nazarin ne bayan ya ba da jawabi game da yadda rashin barci yake shafan nazari.
A ƙarshen jawabin, wata yarinya ta zo wurina, ta ce, "Me ya sa aka gaya mini wannan a yanzu, a shekarar ƙarshe?"
Ta ce babu wanda ya gaya mata game da muhimmancin barci, abin da ya ba ni mamaki", in ji shi a cikin wani rahoto da ya ba wa Telegraph.
Wannan darasi na farko da aka yi a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa ɗaliban yadda yin barci da kyau yake taimaka wa ɗalibai su yi nazari da kuma wasanni, har ma ya taimaka musu su kasance da kwanciyar hankali.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar ɗan adam da kuma shugaban hukumar kula da lafiyar ɗan adam a Harvard Medical School, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan shirin ne bayan ta lura cewa ɗalibai suna barci sosai a mako.
Ana yin nazarin na awa ɗaya, kuma ana yin ayyuka masu kyau.
Wani sashe na nuna wani ɗaki a cikin gida, inda ɗalibai suke shan kofi, suna kallon taga, suna shan takalma, suna karanta littattafai don su koyi game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda yin wasanni zai iya lalacewa idan ba a barci ba, da kuma muhimmancin samun isasshen barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa masu halarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, ciwon jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar makarantar da ke ɗauke da alamun da za su taimaka wa ɗaliban su yi tunani a kan yadda suke yin abubuwa a kowace rana.
Mun san cewa wannan ba zai canja halayen ɗalibai ba.
Amma muna ganin suna da hakkin su san wannan, kamar yadda mutum yake da hakkin ya san illar shan sigari", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adar da ke ɗaukaka waɗanda suke yin barci da dare har yanzu tana nan, ya ce, yana ƙara da cewa fasaha na zamani da matsi mai yawa a kan ɗalibai sun sa rashin barci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Ya ce, samun isashen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama makamin ɗalibai na kāre kansu daga matsi, gajiya, da kuma damuwa - har ma da guje wa kiba, domin rashin barci yana ƙara bukatar abinci a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar mutum don ya kiyaye jikinsa.
Raymond So, ɗalibi ne mai shekara 19 a fannin kimiyyar lissafi daga California, ya taimaka wajen tsara wannan darasi, amma ya zauna a ɗaya daga cikin guraren farfesa a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan nazarin ya sa ya soma tunani sosai kuma ya ƙarfafa shi ya sanar da dukan ɗaliban makarantar cewa za a yi wannan nazarin.
Yana fatan cewa mataki na gaba shi ne a gaya wa dukan masu neman digiri su kammala irin wannan darasi kafin su fara karatu a jami'a.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawara cewa ɗalibai su yi tunanin kafa agogon saurin barci, da kuma farkawa, domin sun san cewa hasken shuɗi da ke fitowa daga allon lantarki da kuma hasken LED yana iya ɓata agogon jiki kuma ya sa barci ya yi wuya.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: alama daga Menga rufe saukar Gerrards mutane
Rangers sun ci gaba da samun matsala a filin wasa yayin da aka raba tawagar Stevens Gerrard, wanda ya yi nasara da Livingston da ci 1-0 bayan Dolly Menga ta ci kwallo.
Ibrox na neman samun nasarar farko a filin wasa bayan nasarar da suka samu a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma Gary Holt ya ba Gerrard kashi na biyu a wasanni 18 da ya buga a matsayin manajan, inda suka ci gaba da cin nasara da maki takwas bayan Hearts, wanda ke kan gaba a gasar Ladbrokes.
Menec ya ci kwallo da minti bakwai kafin a kammala wasan kuma Rangers sun yi rashin kwarin gwiwa kuma ba za su iya gyara ba.
Rangers yanzu sun sauka zuwa matsayi na shida yayin da Livingston ya hau zuwa na uku kuma suna bin Hibernian ne kawai a bambancin burin.
Rangers na iya samun karin matsala bayan da mai tsaron gidan Calum Spence ya bukaci a yi masa jinya saboda ciwon kai bayan an jefa masa wani abu daga kwalkwali mai tsaron gidan.
Gerrard ya yi sau takwas a tawagar da ta yi watsi da Ayr kuma ta kai wasan neman kofin Betfred.
Holt, duk da haka, ya kasance a kan wannan Livi 11 da aka samu daga Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma ya yi farin ciki da yadda 'yan wasan da suka horar da su suka yi nasara a kan abokin hamayyar.
Rangers sun fi kowa samun kwallo, amma Livingston ya samu dama da kwallo da ya samu.
Ya kamata su ci kwallo ne bayan minti biyu da fara wasan lokacin da aka fara watsawa daga Menga Scott Pitman ya zo gaban Allan McGregor, amma ya yi gaba.
Kwanan baya da Keaghan Jacobs ya yi ya kai ga Craig Halkett, amma Alan Lithgow, abokin aikinsa na karewa ya harba shi a gaban filin.
Rangers sun sake dawo da wasan amma sun fi rayuwa cikin bege fiye da imani a wasan su na karshe.
Alfredo Morales ya ji cewa ya kamata a ba shi nasara a wasan da ya yi da Steven Lawless, amma mai shari'a Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da kiran da ya yi.
Rangers sun samu nasarar cin kwallaye biyu a wasan farko amma Liam Kelly, tsohon dan wasan Ibrox, bai bukaci samun nasara ba saboda kare kwallo daga Lassana Coulibaly da kuma sauki daga Ovie Ejaria.
Ko da yake Liv ya samu damar yin wasa a minti na 34 duk da cewa 'yan wasan sun yi nasara, babu wanda zai ce sun cancanci hakan, amma saboda jimirin da suka nuna.
Rangers sun sake kasa yin komai daga dogon kari daga Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai yi karo ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya tura kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya riƙe kwanciyar hankali kuma ya zaɓi aikawa zuwa Menga wanda ya ci gaba da yin wasa da sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi watsi da shi a rabin wasan kuma ya tura Ryan Kent a maimakon Coulibaly kuma canjin ya yi tasiri kusan lokacin da mai tsaron gidan Morelos ya shigo, amma Kelly ya fashe da sauri kuma ya yi tsere don rufe harbi.
Duk da haka, Livingston ya ci gaba da yaudarar baƙi don su yi daidai da irin wasan da suke jin daɗin yin wasa, kuma Lithgow da Halkett sun sami kowane dogon watsawa a kan ƙafafun juna.
Kungiyar Holts za ta iya karawa a kan gaba a minti na karshe, amma McGregor ya yi kyau wajen hana Jacobs damar kafin Lithgow ya ci kwallo daga kusurwa.
Glenn Middleton, mai tsaron gidan Rangers, ya so a sake masa lambar yabo idan ya fadi tare da Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake shi.
Almanak: Mutumin da ya ƙirƙira na'urar kirga abubuwa ta Geiger
Wannan shafi na kalandarmu na "Lahadi da safe" ya fito ne daga ranar 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekara 136 da ta shige, kuma ranar da aka haifi masanin ilimin lissafi Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta auna da kuma auna yawan radiyo, kuma wannan abu ya kai ga wani kayan aiki da ake kira Geiger gauges.
Mai auna Geiger ya sami wurin zama a duniyar kimiyya tun daga lokacin amma kuma ya kasance sananne a cikin al'adun gargajiya, misali a cikin fim din 1950 Bells of Coronado, tare da Roy Rogers da Dale Evans a cikin rawar da ba za a iya tsammani ba a matsayin masana kimiyya:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan a cikin sihiri?"
Rogers: Wannan ma'aunin Geiger ne, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano abubuwa masu guba a cikin Uranium.
Idan ka saka wannan na'urar, za ka iya jin tasirin da atom ke yi a kan duwatsu.
Evans: "Wannan ya sa na yi fushi sosai yanzu!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ya cika shekara 63.
Amma abin da ya yi ya ci gaba da wanzuwa.
