Fim din fim din Johnny English Strikes Again - fim din leken asiri tare da Rowan Atkinson ya tabbatar da rashin karfi
An yi amfani da wannan dabarar wajen neman abubuwan da suka shafi Brexit a duk wani sabon fim da ya shafi Birtaniya, kuma wannan ya zama abin da ya dace da wannan sabon fim din Johnny English - wanda ya fara a 2003 da fim din Johnny English kuma ya sake farfadowa a 2011 da fim din Johnny English Reborn.
Shin wannan abin dariya game da yadda muke da rashin jin daɗi zai zama sabon kayan fitarwa ga ƙasar?
Ko yaya dai, an ba wa Johnny English, mai son magana, mai son yin kuka, da kuma mai son yin magana, izini na biyu don ya ɓata kome - sunansa ya nuna cewa aikinsa ne da aka shirya don a nuna a wasu ƙasashe masu jin Turanci.
Hakika, shi dan leken asiri ne mai basira wanda yake nuna cewa yana da halaye masu ban sha'awa amma yana da ɗan haɗuwa da Clouseau, da Mr. Bean, da ɗan ɗan ɗan mutumin da ya buga waƙa guda ɗaya don waƙar Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na London na 2012.
Hakanan an fara shi ne bisa matafiyi kuma ɗan ƙasa mai ban mamaki wanda Atkinsons ya taɓa yin sa a cikin tallan TV na Barclaycard da aka manta, inda ya rabu da komai cikin rikici.
Akwai abubuwa masu kyau da yawa a cikin wannan sabon fim ɗin Johnny English.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa wurin wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da yake sanye da rigar da ta nuna cewa ya riga ya shiga zamanin dā kuma yana da takardar da ke nuna cewa jirgin sama yana da ƙarfi sosai.
Atkinson a bayyane yake yana nuna kwarewar sa ta wasan kwaikwayo, amma yanayin sa ya zama mai rauni kuma mai ban mamaki, musamman a yanzu da fina-finai masu mahimmanci kamar James Bond da Mission Impossible fina-finai suna ba da izini ga wasan kwaikwayo.
Kamar dai an fi son wa'adin ne ga yara fiye da manya, kuma na ga cewa labarin da Johnny English ya shiga bai kasance mai ban sha'awa ba kuma mai ma'ana kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a cikin Mr. Beans.
Wannan fim din yana nuna cewa, Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya samu nasarar shiga cikin hukumar leken asirin Birtaniya, ya kuma gano duk wani dan leken asirin Birtaniya, abin takaici ga dan leken asirin da ke kan gadon - amma abin takaici Kevin Eldon ya taka rawa kadan.
Wannan shi ne karshe ga Firayim Minista wanda yake da girman kai da kuma rikice-rikice kuma wanda yake da matukar damuwa saboda manyan matsalolin siyasa: Emma Thompson yana yin mafi kyau a matsayinta na mutum wanda ya kamata ya tuna da Theresa May, amma rubutun ba shi da yawa ga mata.
Mashawarcinta ta gaya mata cewa duk masu leƙen asiri da suke aiki suna cikin haɗari kuma dole ne ta sami wanda aka riga aka sanya shi a cikin dutse mai tsarki.
Kuma a nan ne Johnny English ya zo, wanda yanzu shi ne shugaban makarantar da ta fi kyau, amma kuma yana koyar da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: ga wasu ban dariya da English ya yi game da makarantar leƙen asiri da ke kama da fim ɗin School of Rock.
An sake kiran Ingilishi zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa, inda ya haɗu da Bough, tsohon abokin aikinsa, wanda Ben Miller ya sake wasa.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, matarsa ta zama mai kula da jirgin ruwa, amma a cikin wannan rawar da Vicki Pepperdine ke takawa, ba ta iya haskaka haskenta ba.
Mai tsaron gidan da ke lalata duk abin da ke cikin hidimar Mai Martaba yanzu ya sake dawowa kuma ya haɗu da babban mai tsaron gidan Opheliu Bulletovu, wanda Olga Kurylenko ta buga.
A lokaci guda, Firayim Minista yana ta yin amfani da sihiri na wani mai karfin gaske a masana'antar fasaha wanda ya ce zai iya warware matsalar kwamfuta ta Burtaniya: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara tafiya mai ban tsoro: suna kunna gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai ban mamaki wanda ke ba da abinci, suna lalata abubuwa masu ban tsoro yayin da suke yin ɓoye a cikin ƙwararrun masanin Volta, kuma English ya juya komai baya lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da hotunan hoto don nunawa a cikin gidan Volta.
Ba za a iya yin watsi da wannan fim ɗin ba, amma duk da cewa fim ɗin yana da ƙarfi sosai, yana ɗauke da wasu abubuwa na yara.
Abubuwan da ke da kyau.
