A ranar Laraba ne, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da wani talla da jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
