Masana na kasar Sin da na Amurka sun ce, an yi amfani da makircin da kasar Sin ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don cutar da 'yan gudun hijira a jihohin da ke kusa da Iowa, wadanda suka goyi bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
