Tim Berners-Lee, mutumin da ya kirkiro intanet, yana shirin kafa kamfani mai amfani da kwayoyin halitta domin ya yi yaƙi da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin da aka yi na baya-bayan nan na wannan masana'antar, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke kan Solid, wani kayan aiki na buɗewa na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka ajiye bayanan su da kuma mutanen da ke da izinin samun damar kowane bayani.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "sadarwar duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi wannan yanzu", in ji shi game da kamfanin da ke sarrafa kayan lambu.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Shirin yana amfani da fasaha daga Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi ko POD.
Za ka iya samun jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalandarku, kundin kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna cikin burauzar yanar gizo ɗaya, duk a lokaci ɗaya.
Abin da ke na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan sirri shi ne cewa mai amfani yana da cikakken ikon sanin wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke ciki.
Kamfanin ya kira hakan "tallafin mutum ta amfani da bayanai".
