A yanzu, kamfanin ya kunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani mai aikin tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu masu shirye-shirye da aka dauka a matsayin masu aikin kwangila don su yi aiki a kan wannan aikin, da kuma wasu masu shirye-shirye masu sa kai.
