Berners-Lee ya rubuta a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar a kan Medium cewa Inrupt ya yi niyyar samar da makamashi a harkokin kasuwanci da kuma yanayin halittu da zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabon shafin da aka gina a kan Solid.
Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a Intanet a 1994 lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama sanannen murya a tattaunawar da ake yi game da tsaka tsaki na Intane.
Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da zama wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, da Web Foundation of the Open Data Institute, har ma yayin da ya kafa Inrupt.
