Masu gabatar da kara na neman hukuncin kisa kan wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a birnin New York suna neman a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da hannu a harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin New York, wanda ba a taba yanke wa wani hukunci ba a jihar tun shekara ta 1953 don keta dokar tarayya.
An yi zargin cewa Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi hayar motar mota ta Home Depot don kai hari kan mutanen da ke kan titin keke a kan titin mota na West Side Highway a Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da kuma masu hawa keke harin a watan Oktoba.
Don a ba da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas da gangan kuma ya yi wa wasu rauni mai tsanani da gangan, bisa ga sanarwar da aka yi na amincewa da hukuncin kisa, wanda aka shigar a Kotun Kudancin New York.
An rubuta cewa za a iya yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka guda biyu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saipov a kan wasu laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai, wanda ake amfani da shi a yawancin masu gabatar da kara a kan kungiyoyin aikata laifuka.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya kunshi "kwararrun shirye-shirye" kuma sun bayyana ayyukan Sapiov a matsayin "mugu, na zalunci, da rashin mutunci".
"An yanke hukuncin kisa kan Habibullaevic Saipov, sakamakon raunin da ya yi wa jiki, da kuma rashin da ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar.
An kashe mutane biyar da suka yi tafiya daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da jihar Kudancin New York ta sake ɗaukan hukuncin kisa a matsayin magani.
An zargi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu 'yan fashin miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma daga karshe aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
An kashe mutane na ƙarshe a shekara ta 1953 a wata shari'a a birnin New York, a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an same su da laifin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yaƙin Cacar Ƙari shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe ma'auratan a kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wanda aka haifa a Uzbekistan, bai nuna alamar tuba ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, bisa ga takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa jami'an bincike cewa ya ji daɗin abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu ra'ayin kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon kungiyar ISIS a wayarsa, kamar yadda takardar ta nuna.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna masa tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a dukan ƙarar da aka yi masa 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare Saipov, ya ce sun "yi nadama" da hukuncin da kotun ta yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa shawarar da aka yanke na neman hukuncin kisa maimakon amincewa da hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da damar yin gwaji ba, zai kara tsawaita tashin hankali da wannan lamarin ya jawo ga duk wanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
