Dalilin da yasa yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
An yi ta fama da tashin hankali a farkon yaƙin cinikayya tsakanin Amirka da China, kuma ko da yake yaƙin ya yi nisa, ƙulla dangantaka tsakanin ƙasashen biyu zai iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya kaddamar da wani mataki na farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, da suka hada da hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi yawan matakan da aka dauka a wannan makon sun zo ne da sabon haraji da ya kai dala biliyan 200 a kan kayayyaki, kuma ya yi wa kusan rabin kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su Amurka daga China haraji.
A duk lokacin da aka kai hari, Beijing ta yi amfani da wannan kuɗin, kuma kwanan nan ta kafa haraji na kashi 5 zuwa 10 bisa ɗari a kan kayayyakin Amirka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta mayar da martani ga takunkumin ta kuma ba za a yi tsammanin tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu zai yi watsi da shi ba.
Don a sa Washington ta yi kasala, ana bukatar a yi watsi da wasu abubuwa, amma abin kunya ne ga shugaban kasar Sin, Xi Jinping, ya yi kasala a fili ga Amurka.
Amma masana sun ce idan Beijing ta ci gaba da yin wasa, matsin lamba daga yaƙin cinikayya da Amurka na iya yin tasiri mai kyau a kan China a cikin dogon lokaci, ta hanyar rage bukatar tattalin arziki biyu su yi hulɗa da juna.
"Gaskiyar cewa saurin yanke shawara a siyasa a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da koma bayan tattalin arziki a wata ƙasa, a zahiri ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu kallo suka yarda", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike da ke mai da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta New American.
Suriya na shirin dawo da 'yan gudun hijira, in ji ministan harkokin wajen kasar
Kasar Siriya ta ce tana shirye ta amince da 'yan gudun hijirar su koma gida da yardar rai, kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta yi rashin lafiya bayan yaki na shekaru bakwai.
Ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al Moualem ya yi magana a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya inda ya ce yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau, yanayin duniya ya fi kwanciyar hankali da kwanciyar hankali, godiya ga nasarar da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati ta ci gaba da kawo daidaito ta hanyar gina wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka kafa.
An shirya abubuwa domin 'yan gudun hijira su koma ƙasarsu da suka tilasta wa ta'addanci da kuma yanke shawara na tattalin arziki da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma sana'a.
Hukumar ta kiyasta cewa fiye da mutane miliyan biyar da dubu biyar ne suka gudu daga ƙasarsu tun lokacin da aka soma yaƙin a shekara ta 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke zaune a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce hukumomin Syria za su so su taimaka wajen sake gina kasar.
Amma, ya nanata cewa ba za su karɓi taimako na wucin gadi ba ko kuma taimako daga ƙasashen da suka tayar da tawayen.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta hanyar doke tawagar Amurka da maki 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin wasa na Le Golf National a wajen birnin Paris na kasar Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a Turai, kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambin gasar, sa'ad da tawagar da ke karkashin jagorancin Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata don cin Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya fi kowa wahala a gasar, ya buga ƙwallo a saman ruwa a rami na 16, wanda shine par 3, kuma ya rasa wasan sa ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya yi nasara a duk wasanninsa, ya zama dan wasa na farko daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya rasa 5&4 a kan Thorbjorn Olesen daga Denmark, amma yana kan gaba a cikin jerin 'yan wasan Turai.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ke kan gaba a jerin manyan 'yan wasan golf na duniya, ya sha kashi 2 da 1 a kan Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda ya taka leda a gasar Ryder ta karshe.
Sergio Garcia, ɗan ƙasar Spain wanda ya yi wasa a gasar Ryder sau takwas, ya zama ɗan Turai mafi nasara a gasar, inda ya ci nasara sau 25.5 a rayuwarsa.
A yawancin lokaci, ba na kuka, amma a yau, ba abin da zan iya yi.
Ya kasance mai wuya shekara.
Ina godiya sosai ga Thomas don ya zaɓe ni kuma ya ba ni gaskiya.
Ina farin cikin sake samun wannan kyautar.
"Wannan game da tawagar ne, kuma na yi farin cikin taimaka", in ji Garcia mai tausayi bayan lashe gasar Turai.
Ya yi wa kasarsa John Rahm adalci, amma ya doke tsohuwar dan wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods 2&1 a wasan daya a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, mai shekara 23, ya ce, "Na yi alfahari sosai da na doke Tiger Woods, na girma ina kallon sa.
Woods ya rasa dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wannan abin mamaki ne ga wani ɗan wasa da ya taɓa cin kofin duniya sau 14 kuma wanda ya ci Jack Nicklaus ne kawai.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi fama da wannan karshen mako ta samu kanta a filin wasa, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasa mai kyau a duk faɗin gasar.
Jim Furyk, kocin tawagar Amurka, ya ce bayan ya yi takaici da yadda tawagarsa ta yi, "Ina alfahari da su, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
