Dukan 'yan wasansa 12 suna wasa sosai.
Za mu sake haɗuwa, zan yi aiki da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitin Ryder na Bulls kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan mutane 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa shugabansu.
Dole ne ka dauki saman.
